message: Via FDLE Please share this post! A Florida MISSING CHILD Alert has been issued for Naomi Jones, a black female, 12 years old, 5 feet 1 inches tall, 97 pounds, black hair, brown eyes, last seen in the 1000th block of East Johnson Avenue in Pensacola, Florida.  She was last seen wearing a red tank top and American flag denim shorts.  If you have any information on the whereabouts of this child please contact the Escambia County Sheriff's Office at 850-436-9630 or 911.

data.description: The FBI and FDLE are each offering a $10,000 reward for information leading to the recovery of Naomi Jones and the identification, arrest and conviction of the persons responsible. If you have any information call 9-1-1 or the Escambia County Sheriff's Office at 850-436-9630
